        <summary class="faq-question">Do I need technical staff on my team for this to work?</summary>
        <p class="faq-answer">No. We've built systems for businesses run entirely by non-technical people. You'll need someone who understands your business well enough to explain it to us. That's it. We handle the technical side.</p>
      </details>
