        <summary class="faq-question">How does the 100% refund guarantee actually work?</summary>
        <p class="faq-answer">If we deliver the agreed system and your team genuinely isn't satisfied with it, we refund everything you paid. We agree upfront on what success means for your project. If we hit those criteria and you still want a refund, we'll discuss it. If we don't hit them, there's no discussion needed.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">What happens in the first meeting?</summary>
        <p class="faq-answer">It's a 30-minute call. We'll ask about your biggest operational headache, what tools you use, and roughly what budget you're working with. Then we'll be honest about whether AI can help and what it would cost. You won't get a sales pitch. You'll get a direct assessment.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">Does it connect to our existing software?</summary>
        <p class="faq-answer">Usually yes. We connect to most CRM platforms, ERP systems, messaging tools, and e-commerce platforms. If you're on a less common system, we'll check if it has an API. Most business software does. If it doesn't, we'll tell you upfront rather than discovering it mid-project.</p>
